name: ERIC
description:
Hey,
My name is Eric and I am a rescued cat living with A lovely soul who's taking care of me and a few other rescued cat in her family home, She is individual and uses her own saving to buy food and medication for us, By purchasing my NFT you will help to support us and more stray cats who lives in the street.

We love and support stray animals. The sales profit of this collection will be used to support a few individual shelter who does rescue animals. To see the cats story visit @edward__angel on Instagram.
